        Balconies and Terraces in Brisbane Apartments: How Outdoor Space Drives Sale Price
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        In Brisbane's apartment market, the balcony or terrace is often the single feature that separates a strong sale from a slow one. Here is how depth, orientation, privacy, and connection to living spaces shape buyer demand and price.
      </p>
